CREATE OR REPLACE PACKAGE BODY CHTR.DA_PARTY_CHANNEL_INST

FUNCTION add (
process_rec IN pkg_logging.t_process_rec
,party_id IN NUMBER
,audit_user IN VARCHAR2
) RETURN NUMBER
IS
l_return_pk NUMBER;
BEGIN

chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'begin da_party_channel_inst.add(fx), parms=' || party_id || '|' || audit_user || '|');
INSERT INTO chtr.t_party_channel_inst a
(
a.party_channel_instance_id
,a.party_id
,a.record_stat
,a.created_dttm
,a.created_by
,a.modified_dttm
,a.modified_by
)
VALUES
(
chtr.s_party_channel_instance_id.NEXTVAL
,add.party_id
,'A'
,SYSTIMESTAMP
,add.audit_user
,NULL
,NULL
) RETURNING a.party_channel_instance_id INTO l_return_pk;
chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'end da_party_channel_inst.add(fx)');
RETURN l_return_pk;

END add;
